Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.04,0:02:17.09,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,I've never forgotten.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.09,0:02:20.05,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Don't put me on the same level as\Nsomeone who only even thinks about having fun!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.05,0:02:22.29,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,And the way you put it really pisses me off!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.76,0:02:25.43,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,How do you win a drawing?
