Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.55,0:02:27.97,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Love!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.22,0:02:29.10,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Yeah, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.10,0:02:31.43,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,I'm just a loveless woman.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.43,0:02:32.02,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.02,0:02:33.23,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,If you jot down the usual stuff...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.23,0:02:35.02,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,...you're not going to win.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.77,0:02:37.65,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,What do you put on yours?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.65,0:02:39.57,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Stuff that'll help me win.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.57,0:02:40.74,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,How?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.74,0:02:43.28,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Good handwriting is a fundamental must.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.28,0:02:47.62,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,You have to design a postcard \Nthat just begs to be drawn.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.62,0:02:48.62,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Like what?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.62,0:02:50.24,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Like...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.24,0:02:53.33,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Use a fluorescent marker to draw \Na border around the postcard.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.29,0:02:55.80,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,That'll stand out.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.21,0:03:00.09,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Then you add a picture related to the prize.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.09,0:03:01.67,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,A picture, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.01,0:03:04.59,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,I can't draw very well though.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.59,0:03:06.09,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,In that case...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.64,0:03:09.61,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,...just send in as many entries as you can.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.68,0:03:11.93,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,I can probably handle that.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.93,0:03:12.89,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.89,0:03:15.19,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,No matter how many you send...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.19,0:03:19.86,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,...write each one out without using a printer.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.86,0:03:21.69,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,And send out a hundred each time.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.69,0:03:22.74,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,A hundred?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.74,0:03:24.78,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Isn't that normal?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.78,0:03:26.53,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Wouldn't that cost a lot?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.53,0:03:28.95,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,You're fighting for something you want.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.95,0:03:31.37,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,That calls for passion and guts!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.37,0:03:34.29,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,But wouldn't it be cheaper just to buy it then?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.29,0:03:37.46,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Some things in this world can't be bought with money.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.35,0:03:40.38,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Can you fit a hundred postcards in a mailbox?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.38,0:03:42.88,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,You don't send them all at once...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.88,0:03:45.68,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,...but a few here and a few there.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.68,0:03:47.43,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,And over the course of a few days.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.55,0:03:51.26,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Depending on who's running the drawing...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.26,0:03:53.77,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,...you might get caught.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.81,0:03:57.15,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Well, sometimes you're \Nbetter off without the tricky stuff.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.15,0:03:58.90,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,And sometimes it's the exact opposite.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.90,0:04:00.36,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,So what do we do?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.36,0:04:01.02,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Like I said...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.23,0:04:01.77,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Love!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.77,0:04:02.65,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Yeah, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.82,0:04:04.78,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Anyway, if you want to win...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.78,0:04:07.95,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,...glance through free newspapers and flyers...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.95,0:04:11.99,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,...and look for drawings that\Nprobably aren't going to attract many people.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.99,0:04:14.08,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,You'll have a high chance of winning.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.79,0:04:15.75,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,I'll give it a try!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.75,0:04:17.42,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Where's the love in that?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.88,0:04:22.50,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,You know, for twins...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.63,0:04:25.10,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,...you don't look anything like each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.84,0:04:28.51,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,That's 'cause we're two-egg twins.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.51,0:04:31.10,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,So it's more like comparing sisters.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.60,0:04:33.89,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,One-egg twins look exactly the same...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.89,0:04:35.14,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,...but two-egg twins can be...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.14,0:04:37.10,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,...pretty different in appearance and personality.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.35,0:04:38.64,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.69,0:04:40.81,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Tsukasa is laid-back...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.81,0:04:41.81,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,...but Kagami is pretty psycho.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.81,0:04:42.77,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,What was that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.48,0:04:45.73,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,If you had the same hairstyles with the same ribbons...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.73,0:04:47.57,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,...you might end up looking the same.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.90,0:04:49.24,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Kona-chan!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.80,0:04:50.32,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,No good.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.32,0:04:51.74,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Kagami could never be the cutesy type.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.74,0:04:52.62,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Zip it!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.62,0:04:55.20,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Don't insult me with your weird fantasies!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.50,0:04:57.28,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Can you use telepathy?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.96,0:04:58.64,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,You know.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.64,0:04:59.62,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,With twins...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.62,0:05:01.50,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Even when they're raised separately...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.50,0:05:06.38,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,...they end up having similar \Nlifestyles and significant others.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.38,0:05:08.59,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,And sometimes they end up \Nmarrying another pair of twins.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.76,0:05:10.76,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,And when one of them is in danger...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.76,0:05:14.72,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,...the other one can sense it \Nfrom a completely different place.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.93,0:05:17.27,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,There are all kinds of mysterious phenomena.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.27,0:05:19.35,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,So can't you use telepathy?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.35,0:05:20.65,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Give it a spin.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.65,0:05:21.19,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Abracadabra!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.19,0:05:23.31,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,You read way too much manga.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.31,0:05:24.77,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Same with ManaKana...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.77,0:05:26.07,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,ManaKana?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.07,0:05:29.32,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,I heard that they have a few differences.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.32,0:05:31.82,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,By the way, Mana is the careful one...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.82,0:05:33.53,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,...and Kana is the optimistic one.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.53,0:05:37.08,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,And apparently they sound \Na little different when they sing.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.08,0:05:37.87,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,That reminds me...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.08,0:05:42.29,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,ManaKana thought they were \Ntwo-egg twins for a long time...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.29,0:05:45.49,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,...but they recently learned that \Nthey were actually one-egg twins.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.05,0:05:47.21,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Seriously?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.23,0:05:48.84,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Is it really that surprising?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.01,0:05:51.22,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,The definitions for one-egg and two-egg twins...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.22,0:05:53.09,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,...have changed recently.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.28,0:05:56.69,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Which means that you two could be one-egg twins.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.06,0:05:59.33,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Your identical traits would be...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.39,0:06:02.48,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,You both like sweets, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.06,0:06:03.95,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Love 'em.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.95,0:06:04.61,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,I guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.86,0:06:06.36,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,You're both left-handed.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.19,0:06:08.11,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.28,0:06:09.32,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,What's your favorite color?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.57,0:06:10.36,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,White maybe.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.49,0:06:11.15,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Black.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.15,0:06:13.03,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,The same colors as your souls.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.03,0:06:14.43,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,What was that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.00,0:06:21.96,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,All this talk about eggs and black\Nand white cookies has made me hungry.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.96,0:06:24.04,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Nobody was talking about food.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.21,0:06:32.13,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,It's suffocating in here.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.43,0:06:34.84,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,We just got on and I've already broken a sweat.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.84,0:06:36.93,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,It's that time of year.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.05,0:06:38.76,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Hot...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.81,0:06:41.24,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,They haven't turned on the air conditioning yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.90,0:06:46.98,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,H-Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.98,0:06:49.73,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Hot...
