Dialogue: 1,0:06:49.73,0:06:53.36,ls_fo,,0,0,0,,{\fs20\shad0\fn@Kozuka Gothic Pr6N R\c&H313133&\pos(544.667,618.833)\frz10.44}After a long courtship,\Nwe, Kiyotaka Narumi\Nand Yui Kobayakawa,\Nwill be tying the knot\Non June **.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.73,0:06:53.36,ls_fo,,0,0,0,,{\fs28\blur0.4\shad0\fn@Kozuka Gothic Pr6N R\b0\c&H313133&\pos(434.572,401.072)\frz10.26}Soujiro Izumi\NKonata
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.73,0:06:53.36,ls_fo,,0,0,0,,{\fs20\shad0\blur0.4\fn@Kozuka Gothic Pr6N R\c&H313133&\pos(544.667,618.833)\frz10.44}After a long courtship,\Nwe, Kiyotaka Narumi\Nand Yui Kobayakawa,\Nwill be tying the knot\Non June **.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.86,0:06:53.07,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Ladybug Samba, punk version.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.82,0:06:59.83,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,One of my cousins is getting married this month.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.91,0:07:02.71,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,So she'll be a June bride.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.71,0:07:03.75,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Sounds wonderful.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.75,0:07:05.17,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,How does this...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.37,0:07:10.09,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,...wet and gloomy season \Nsupposedly signify happiness?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.76,0:07:16.30,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Why does getting married in June make you happy?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.18,0:07:19.51,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,The name June...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.51,0:07:21.22,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,...is generally said to be...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.22,0:07:23.85,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,...derived from the name of the Roman goddess, Juno.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.85,0:07:24.73,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,In Greek mythology...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.73,0:07:27.15,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,...Juno is known as Hera...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.15,0:07:29.40,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,...the goddess of marriage and fertility.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.82,0:07:33.65,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Which is why those who get married\Nin Hera's month, the month of June...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.65,0:07:36.45,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,...are said to receive her protection and blessing.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.28,0:07:39.99,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,But wasn't Hera Zeus's wife?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.99,0:07:41.45,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Yes, that's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.66,0:07:44.75,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,I have this image of Hera being extremely jealous...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.75,0:07:47.25,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,...so I'm not feeling this happy thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.00,0:07:48.54,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.88,0:07:52.09,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Would you rather wear \Na dress or a kimono for your wedding?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.30,0:07:54.42,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,I would wear a dress.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.42,0:07:57.26,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,It's been my dream since I was a child.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.09,0:08:00.22,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,I'd also go with a dress.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.22,0:08:02.43,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,But a kimono would also be nice...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.10,0:08:05.78,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,I wanna wear both!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.39,0:08:09.90,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,They have miniskirts and \Nreally colorful dresses these days.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.82,0:08:12.57,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,A miniskirt wedding dress?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.57,0:08:16.07,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,It'd look really cute with lots of frills on the hem.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.24,0:08:17.45,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Lots of dreams!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.45,0:08:18.78,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Lots of frills!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.99,0:08:19.95,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.95,0:08:21.95,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,You're Angel Salvia.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.95,0:08:22.54,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.54,0:08:25.28,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Your hair makes you look more like Daisy.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.28,0:08:28.56,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,So a yellow top and miniskirt it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.04,0:08:30.92,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Tsukasa-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.92,0:08:32.55,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,You'd probably look good in a miniskirt.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.55,0:08:33.55,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.55,0:08:34.71,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Your dress is important...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.71,0:08:37.34,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,...but the person you're getting \Nmarried to is also important.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.51,0:08:39.14,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,A childhood friend?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.14,0:08:40.80,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Or a rich lady?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.80,0:08:42.89,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Tough choice to make.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.89,0:08:44.89,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,One has lots of money...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.89,0:08:48.34,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,...and the ability to cast Beho*mi and l***zun.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.75,0:08:50.10,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,But as far as feelings are concerned...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.10,0:08:51.77,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Bianca hands down!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.77,0:08:52.98,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Oh, Kagami.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.98,0:08:54.48,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,You're the true love type, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.48,0:08:56.40,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,I thought you'd go for the money.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.99,0:08:58.44,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,No comeback, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.07,0:09:02.53,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Yo, Konata.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.49,0:09:06.54,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,I've got a question about a \Ngame I borrowed the other day.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.54,0:09:07.16,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.16,0:09:09.00,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Hold it right there, Kagaminya.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.12,0:09:12.50,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Isn't it more fun when you figure it out yourself?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.29,0:09:14.46,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,You have a point.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.46,0:09:15.30,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Yep, yep.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.42,0:09:18.59,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Since you understand that \Nyou should do things yourself...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.59,0:09:20.80,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,...you'll do your own homework from now on, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.97,0:09:25.35,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Don't the detectives in manga and TV shows...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.35,0:09:28.35,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,...run into an awful lot of murders?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.52,0:09:30.44,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Like in Conan or Kindaichi.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.44,0:09:33.40,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,There wouldn't be a story otherwise.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.40,0:09:34.19,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.19,0:09:36.32,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Couldn't they just solve normal cases?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.32,0:09:37.32,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Normal?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.34,0:09:41.38,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Like travel around Japan in search of missing persons.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.38,0:09:44.28,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Tailing people would translate well into a game.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.28,0:09:46.45,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,With plenty of thrill and suspense.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.45,0:09:47.58,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,I guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.58,0:09:51.04,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,You could also conduct \Ninvestigations into unfaithful wives.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.04,0:09:52.88,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Or look for pets that ran away?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.88,0:09:54.34,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Yep, yep!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.34,0:09:57.07,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,But would that be fun to watch?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.51,0:09:59.55,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Probably no fun at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.55,0:10:00.34,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.34,0:10:01.38,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Also...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.38,0:10:02.84,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Cases in real life...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.84,0:10:05.76,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,...don't really use any brilliant tricks...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.76,0:10:07.56,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,...like the ones you find in manga and TV shows.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.64,0:10:10.02,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,I guess not.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.02,0:10:14.41,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Fabricated fingerprints that can't be\Ndetected through a luminol reaction.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.41,0:10:16.94,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Stuff that's a step ahead of forensic labs.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.94,0:10:17.65,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.65,0:10:20.24,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Anything too good might lead to copycats.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.24,0:10:22.24,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Or be too sensitive for broadcast.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.24,0:10:23.70,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Ah, or that...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.70,0:10:27.87,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,The really hard cases end without\Nanyone realizing they happened or go...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.87,0:10:28.54,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,...unsolved.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.54,0:10:30.96,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,That'd be wrong in so many ways!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.12,0:10:34.83,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Don't you hate how it's been \Nconstantly raining the past few days?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.83,0:10:36.54,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,You're right...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.42,0:10:42.38,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,And I used to like rain...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.38,0:10:43.93,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,You get soaked...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.93,0:10:45.76,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,...and you can't hang clothes out to dry...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.76,0:10:47.62,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,...so I've never really liked it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.06,0:10:49.93,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Why did you like rain, Kona-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.22,0:10:55.02,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Because baseball games would be\Ncanceled and I'd get to watch anime.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.02,0:10:56.23,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.23,0:10:58.07,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Sounds just like something you would say.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.07,0:11:00.99,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,They have a lot more dome stadiums now.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.61,0:11:06.91,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Is something wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.03,0:11:13.12,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,You often see idiots and geniuses\Ngoing to the same school in anime...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.33,0:11:14.75,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Cease that immediately.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.75,0:11:15.80,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Bite me!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.80,0:11:17.75,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Get lost, neener-neener!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.88,0:11:20.34,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Isn't that actually kinda strange?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.34,0:11:21.46,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,If you put it that way...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.78,0:11:22.88,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,...in some recent anime...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.88,0:11:26.93,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,...the teacher looks the same age as the students.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.93,0:11:28.47,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Or even younger.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.64,0:11:29.43,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Teach.
