Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.31,0:11:34.98,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,The world's always been interested in watching...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.98,0:11:38.40,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,...the gap between physical age and mental age.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.40,0:11:39.19,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Don't get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.36,0:11:42.03,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,You shouldn't question it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.03,0:11:44.99,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,In fact, wouldn't a student who's\Nreally different from everyone else...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.99,0:11:47.03,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,...be the real mystery?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.74,0:11:49.58,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.58,0:11:51.99,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,I agree one hundred percent.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.29,0:11:53.95,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,I shouldn't be saying this...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.95,0:11:56.54,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,...but I don't know how \Nyou got into this school, Konata.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.79,0:11:58.60,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,You're good at putting stuff \Noff till the night before...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.60,0:12:00.54,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,...so you didn't study \Nuntil the night before, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.67,0:12:06.13,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,{\i1}What?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.13,0:12:07.47,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,{\i1}You mean she really did?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.64,0:12:08.14,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Nah.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.14,0:12:10.96,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Well, I couldn't have pulled it off in one night.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.96,0:12:12.22,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,That gave me a scare.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.38,0:12:14.98,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,But I'm impressed that you actually kept studying.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.98,0:12:17.77,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Did a quiz game come out for DS or something?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.94,0:12:20.64,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,My dad set some conditions.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.64,0:12:21.98,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,A D-rank would mean a Pippin.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.98,0:12:23.61,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,A C-rank would mean a 3DO.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.61,0:12:25.65,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,A B-rank would mean a PS2.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.65,0:12:26.65,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Papa Izumi.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.65,0:12:29.24,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,{\i1}You really know how to deal with your daughter, huh?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.41,0:12:30.78,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,I've been wondering...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.00,0:12:39.12,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Isn't the real mystery how \NTsukasa's in the same school as us?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.12,0:12:41.59,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,She said it without even blinking!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.59,0:12:43.71,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,{\an3}Woo-hoo!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.13,0:12:45.84,ls_alt,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Come back in ten years!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.71,0:12:46.63,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,{\an3}I won again!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.92,0:12:45.80,ls_alt,,0,0,0,,{\an1}Curses!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.80,0:12:47.51,ls_alt,,0,0,0,,{\an1}I can't beat her at fighting games.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.51,0:12:48.93,ls_alt,,0,0,0,,{\an1}She's spent way more time than I have.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.97,0:12:52.10,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Challenge to me a different game if you want.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.06,0:12:54.35,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Sure about that?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.35,0:12:56.10,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Then next is...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.23,0:12:57.77,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,A quiz game!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.35,0:12:59.44,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,N-No way...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.44,0:13:02.23,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,I lost to Konata in a game of knowledge?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.23,0:13:03.19,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Unbelievable...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.07,0:13:05.19,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Don't tell me...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.19,0:13:07.53,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,{\i1\an3}...she memorized the question order?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.49,0:13:07.64,ls_alt,,0,0,0,,{\an1}Humiliated.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.64,0:13:10.53,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,{\an3\i1}Her memory's incredible when it comes to gaming.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.95,0:13:12.20,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,What should we play next?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.20,0:13:13.74,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Don't be in such a hurry.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.24,0:13:16.08,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Huh? That's weird.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.08,0:13:19.33,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Didn't you have a really easy party game?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.33,0:13:22.58,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,How do you know all the games I have?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.58,0:13:25.55,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,You could probably beat me at that one.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.38,0:13:28.03,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,It just stunk!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.51,0:13:31.51,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,You've barely eaten any snacks, Kagami.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.51,0:13:33.51,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Usually, you wolf them down.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.51,0:13:35.53,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,There's no real reason for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.53,0:13:36.39,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.39,0:13:38.64,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Dieting for summer?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.64,0:13:40.56,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,It's not like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.69,0:13:42.81,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Not like you have anyone \Nto show your swimsuit off to.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.81,0:13:43.56,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Shut it!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.56,0:13:44.57,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,It's none of your business!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.86,0:13:45.52,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Oh, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.52,0:13:47.65,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Weren't you guys born on Tanabata?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.65,0:13:49.53,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Isn't your birthday soon?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.53,0:13:50.57,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,What about it?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.57,0:13:53.14,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,You remembered our birthday.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.62,0:13:55.12,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Seventeen, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.12,0:13:57.29,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Seventeen's right before the big one.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.29,0:13:59.04,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,What does that mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.04,0:14:00.58,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,In the year before a critical year...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.58,0:14:03.77,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,...unlucky things begin to happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.49,0:14:06.63,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,As our birthday approaches...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.63,0:14:08.74,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,...I'm getting worried...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.74,0:14:10.84,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,...so I bought a bunch of wards...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.84,0:14:13.14,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,...and power stones.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.34,0:14:15.01,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,That sounds like fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.01,0:14:16.22,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Sure is!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.22,0:14:17.97,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,I couldn't stop buying them.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.97,0:14:18.81,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,And like...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.81,0:14:20.48,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,We have wards against rage at our place.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.48,0:14:21.23,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Er, no.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.23,0:14:22.60,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Wards against evil.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.60,0:14:24.24,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Wards against rage, hah.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.65,0:14:25.61,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Like...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.61,0:14:29.49,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,We ensure safe pregnancy and protect\Nyou from traffic accidents at the same time!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.49,0:14:30.61,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Yeah, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.78,0:14:32.06,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Oh, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.06,0:14:35.68,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Did you know that your birthday is Ponytail Day?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.03,0:14:37.24,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,I had no idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.24,0:14:39.66,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,But why July 7th?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.66,0:14:43.50,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Because Vega from the Tanabata legend had a ponytail.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.50,0:14:45.50,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Sounds like a stretch.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.50,0:14:48.96,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,There's a Japan Ponytail Society...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.96,0:14:54.61,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,...and they give an award every year to a celebrity who they think would look good with a ponytail.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.22,0:14:56.51,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Really...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.51,0:15:00.02,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,But I have a feeling that anyone \Nwould look good with a ponytail.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.18,0:15:01.64,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Sure about that?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.65,0:15:09.69,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,My hair's the shortest...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.69,0:15:10.73,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,...so it's barely a ponytail.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.73,0:15:13.90,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,But a little ponytail's pretty cute.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.90,0:15:15.78,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Yours also looks good, Kona-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.78,0:15:18.37,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,You could go with that on an everyday basis.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.37,0:15:19.83,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Think so?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.58,0:15:21.69,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.17,0:15:28.54,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,S-Sis also...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.54,0:15:29.59,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Kagami's is...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.59,0:15:30.34,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Fine!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.75,0:15:31.51,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,I get the idea!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.51,0:15:33.30,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,I'll undo it!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.30,0:15:34.80,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,All manly like a warrior.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.80,0:15:36.22,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Sorry about that!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.74,0:15:41.39,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Don't drunks often wear ties around their head?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.39,0:15:43.31,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Is that supposed to mean something?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.31,0:15:44.27,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Oh, that?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.56,0:15:46.15,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Isn't that just when the guy loosens the tie...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.15,0:15:48.15,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,...and tries to pull it off over his head...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.15,0:15:50.11,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,...but it gets stuck?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.78,0:15:53.03,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,In that case...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.03,0:15:56.57,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,...it's a lot weirder that \Nthey're always carrying a takeout box.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.57,0:15:57.87,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Takeout box?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.87,0:16:00.28,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,The thing Kato-chan from the Drifters carries.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.91,0:16:02.45,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,I'm not getting it...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.45,0:16:04.12,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Drunks these days...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.45,0:16:09.29,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,...pretty much always have a tie around\Ntheir head and a takeout box in their hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.29,0:16:10.34,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.34,0:16:14.30,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,I hope Vega and Altair meet this year.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.46,0:16:16.26,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Shine. Shine. Shine.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.26,0:16:19.05,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Hope those rage wards of yours can deliver a miracle.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.05,0:16:20.39,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Mind your own business.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.47,0:16:24.90,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,They're giving away all varieties \Nof QUO cards at Comp Festival.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.90,0:16:25.87,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Oh, yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.87,0:16:27.90,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,You're always collecting QUO cards...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.90,0:16:29.35,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,...but do you ever use them?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.02,0:16:31.22,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,I don't.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.61,0:16:33.23,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Then why spend the effort?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.44,0:16:35.61,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Isn't it natural to want any item...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.61,0:16:37.61,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,...related to a series you like?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.61,0:16:39.53,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,As a fan. As a collector.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.53,0:16:40.57,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Not really...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.57,0:16:41.87,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,...if you're never gonna use them...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.87,0:16:43.54,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,You can't use them!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.54,0:16:45.25,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,You have to take good care of them!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.25,0:16:49.37,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,It really pisses me off when I see someone use one.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.37,0:16:51.79,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,You're not supposed to use these things!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.79,0:16:55.63,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Much less auction them off or sell them.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.63,0:16:57.26,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Using them makes you a surefire failure...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.26,0:16:59.09,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,...as a fan and as a collector!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.09,0:17:01.93,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,I really can't say anything when you're so worked up.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.14,0:17:05.60,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,In my case, I at least need three.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.60,0:17:07.60,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,One for preservation.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.60,0:17:09.98,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,I keep it in a special case.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.98,0:17:13.15,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Then one to take out occasionally to look at.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.15,0:17:14.07,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,What's the last one for?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.07,0:17:14.82,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,An extra.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.82,0:17:15.73,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.73,0:17:21.50,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Don't you always want two \Nor three of something you like?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.74,0:17:24.41,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Yeah, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.41,0:17:25.24,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,You don't.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.24,0:17:26.83,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,I'm just a geek.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.83,0:17:27.62,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,A weirdo.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.62,0:17:28.33,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.33,0:17:31.63,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,I kind of understand what you're saying.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.38,0:17:34.67,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,You'd expect Tsukasa to be popular with guys...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.67,0:17:36.63,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,...but I've never heard anything like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.55,0:17:40.34,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Tsukasa's a little plain and doesn't really stand out.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.30,0:17:43.85,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Isn't it because she's got a \Nscary sister guarding her like a hawk?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.85,0:17:45.35,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Did you say something?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.56,0:17:47.52,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,I'm not sure if I'm really plain...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.52,0:17:50.19,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,...or it's more that Kona-chan \Nand Yuki-chan are really unique.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.35,0:17:53.44,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Miyuki knows all kinds of things.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.44,0:17:54.23,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,And she's pretty.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.23,0:17:55.36,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Has a good figure.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.36,0:17:56.57,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Wears glasses.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.57,0:17:57.61,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Hates the dentist.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.61,0:17:58.11,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Clumsy.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.11,0:17:59.28,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Naturally clueless.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.53,0:17:59.24,ls_alt,,0,0,0,,Hey now.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.24,0:18:01.20,ls_alt,,0,0,0,,You kinda derailed there?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.41,0:18:04.45,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,But it's true that I haven't \Nheard anything about Miyuki.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.45,0:18:05.91,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Maybe it's because she's so pretty...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.91,0:18:07.37,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,...that everyone's afraid to approach her?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.37,0:18:08.87,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,I doubt that.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.87,0:18:09.71,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,She's kind...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.71,0:18:11.08,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,...and really good at helping others.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.08,0:18:12.33,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,That's true.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.33,0:18:14.63,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Maybe a lot of guys ask her out.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.63,0:18:16.38,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,But she turns them down?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.38,0:18:17.71,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Turns them down, huh...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.71,0:18:18.30,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Nah.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.30,0:18:20.88,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Maybe she doesn't realize that they're asking her out.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.88,0:18:22.51,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,That's possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.51,0:18:24.51,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Yuki-chan can be a little clueless...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.51,0:18:26.85,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,...so an indirect approach might not work.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.85,0:18:30.60,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Man, the guys in your class are hopeless.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.60,0:18:32.81,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Doesn't a single one of them have the guts...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.81,0:18:35.65,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,...to confess his passionate feelings to Miyuki?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.65,0:18:36.94,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Guess not...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.94,0:18:39.61,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,We don't have enough maniacs in our class.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.49,0:18:43.91,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Miyuki-san's type is usually a bigger hit with maniacs.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.37,0:18:47.01,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Maniacs, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.83,0:18:48.74,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.74,0:18:49.37,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.37,0:18:51.58,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,It's already this late.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.58,0:18:53.72,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,I'll need to excuse myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.72,0:18:55.06,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.06,0:18:58.85,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Please continue to enjoy yourselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.17,0:19:00.96,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Then I'll excuse myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.47,0:19:02.67,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,See you later!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.67,0:19:04.26,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Buh-bye.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.76,0:19:06.93,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Anyway...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.93,0:19:08.72,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Going on with the story...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.72,0:19:10.31,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,...that person was actually...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.43,0:19:12.10,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,O-Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.41,0:19:14.39,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,I-I'm terribly sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.39,0:19:15.73,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Yay!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.98,0:19:17.56,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,I-I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.56,0:19:18.90,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Man, oh, man...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.90,0:19:20.61,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Doesn't that always happen?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.61,0:19:22.86,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,I did it the other day.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.86,0:19:24.11,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,So did I.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.28,0:19:26.78,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Everybody at least does it once.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.78,0:19:27.99,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Right, Konata?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.99,0:19:28.88,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,I haven't.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.41,0:19:32.50,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,That was what you call \Nan element of turning people on.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.83,0:19:33.79,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Miyuki-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.79,0:19:35.00,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Good job!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.67,0:19:42.05,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Good lucky!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.17,0:19:42.88,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.88,0:19:46.13,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Today's another whoo-whoo \Nhappy episode of Lucky Channel!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.55,0:19:48.64,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,I'm your navigator, Akira Kogami.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.64,0:19:49.10,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,And...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.10,0:19:49.97,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Uh.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.97,0:19:52.72,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,I'm Akira-sama's assistant, Minoru Shiraishi.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.72,0:19:53.52,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,It's a pleasure.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.68,0:19:54.64,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Okay, okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.64,0:19:56.73,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,The two of us have now done this...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.73,0:19:57.77,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Ta-da!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.02,0:19:59.65,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Three times after today!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.65,0:20:01.23,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,How do you feel about it, Shiraishi-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.23,0:20:02.28,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Have you gotten used to it?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.28,0:20:03.07,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.28,0:20:04.32,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Not yet...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.32,0:20:05.11,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,So sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.07,0:20:10.78,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,It feels like Shiraishi-san hasn't opened up to me yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.20,0:20:13.41,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,And it looks like we're sitting further apart than usual.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.91,0:20:16.29,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Is this what they mean by emotional distance?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.29,0:20:16.75,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Sob.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.42,0:20:19.38,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Th-Th-That's not true!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.38,0:20:19.96,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Shuffle.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.96,0:20:20.75,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.75,0:20:23.05,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Let's get rollin'!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.38,0:20:24.09,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.09,0:20:27.05,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,We've got something the fans will love today!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.05,0:20:28.05,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Guess what?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.05,0:20:31.18,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,We'll be doing our first\Nintroduction for a member of the regular cast!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.18,0:20:32.35,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Da! Da-da-dum!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.35,0:20:33.31,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Okay, uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.31,0:20:35.85,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,We'll be introducing Miyuki Takara-san today.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.98,0:20:37.10,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Let's see...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.10,0:20:41.44,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,The class representative, well-mannered, kn—
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.44,0:20:42.48,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Knowledgeable.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.48,0:20:43.57,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Knowledgeable...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.57,0:20:46.11,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,...in both literary and culinary arts. A perfect person.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.11,0:20:46.82,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Shiraishi-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.99,0:20:49.20,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,You know Miyuki-san, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.20,0:20:50.87,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,But of course!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.87,0:20:52.62,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,She's so wonderful, yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.62,0:20:54.20,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,First, there's her glasses!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.20,0:20:55.91,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,And then she's pretty as a button.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.91,0:20:57.37,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,With those looks...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.37,0:21:00.17,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,...you'd expect her to be hard to approach...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.17,0:21:03.00,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,...but she's actually a friendly person...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.00,0:21:05.92,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,I wish you'd talk that much on the radio show...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.26,0:21:09.68,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,You can't stop talking when it's about Miyuki-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.18,0:21:10.89,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.89,0:21:12.14,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,That's not it...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.14,0:21:13.22,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Well, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.22,0:21:15.10,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Miyuki Takara-san, is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.10,0:21:16.48,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,A pretty face.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.48,0:21:17.64,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,With large breasts.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.64,0:21:19.39,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,And various other turn-ons.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.56,0:21:21.94,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Isn't she so lucky to be a pretty character?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.35,0:21:21.94,ls_alt,,0,0,0,,Akira-sama, that's a little...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.94,0:21:23.82,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,The maniacs loves her.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.57,0:21:24.48,ls_alt,,0,0,0,,Uh, maniacs is a little...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.82,0:21:24.48,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,But you know...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.48,0:21:27.61,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,If it's maniacs you want, \NI'm a huge hit with those lolicons...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.61,0:21:29.28,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Too bad!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.28,0:21:31.03,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,It's time to say goodbye!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.03,0:21:32.16,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,And so...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.16,0:21:39.04,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Send us any questions or \Ncomments about the show please!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.50,0:21:41.17,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Please look forward to next time.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.17,0:21:42.75,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,See ya!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.84,0:21:45.50,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,So what's she really like?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.92,0:21:47.01,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Exactly the same.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.01,0:21:48.05,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.05,0:21:51.22,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Doesn't she like smoke a pack at a time backstage?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.22,0:21:53.18,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,No worry of that. She isn't you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.18,0:21:58.60,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,That was fun!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.60,0:22:00.31,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,A unique song.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.31,0:22:03.48,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,I'd like to hear a song that \Nnormal people can enjoy already.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.02,0:22:05.98,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,You know the next one, Kagami.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.57,0:22:08.60,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Guess it from the intro!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.60,0:22:10.86,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,It's not another weird song, is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.45,0:22:15.58,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,What was this song again?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.58,0:22:16.83,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Don't know...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.83,0:22:17.49,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Kagami.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.49,0:22:18.50,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,The answer is...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.41,0:22:21.08,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,It's from FMP. FMP.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.00,0:22:24.13,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,And it's Kagami's favorite...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.13,0:22:25.45,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Fumoffu!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.45,0:22:26.34,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Really...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.34,0:22:28.41,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,I-I just read the novels...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.41,0:22:29.79,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,...and got a little hooked.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.39,0:22:34.93,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,You're really good, Kona-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.93,0:22:37.18,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,You can also sound like an adult.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.18,0:22:39.76,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Isn't she just doing an imitation?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.02,0:22:43.65,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,So?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.65,0:22:45.65,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,What are you two going to sing?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.31,0:22:48.15,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,I wonder if there's anything I can sing...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.15,0:22:50.28,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,I don't know very many songs...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.28,0:22:51.74,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Anything works.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.74,0:22:52.90,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Look at Konata.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.95,0:22:55.74,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Just sing what you want to!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.74,0:22:56.45,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.45,0:22:57.99,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Then I'll have a look.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.99,0:23:00.25,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,I'm not very confident about my singing...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.25,0:23:01.66,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,It's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.66,0:23:03.29,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,We're the only ones who'll hear you.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.29,0:23:04.79,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Just take it easy.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.79,0:23:06.33,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.33,0:23:07.29,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,In that case...
