Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.81,0:23:28.02,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Well, next time on Lucky Star:
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.02,0:23:28.77,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,I'm Tsukasa.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.77,0:23:29.48,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Guess what?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.48,0:23:33.45,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,I laughed so hard the other day that I couldn't breathe.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.45,0:23:34.32,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Then at school one morning...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.65,0:23:36.04,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,I'm already out of time?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.04,0:23:36.66,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Next time:
